That also reframes the cognitive prosthetic.

Most prosthetics replace loss.

The Pantheon prosthetic is closer to an augmentation of continuity.

Not:

Remember for me.

But:

Help me remain in flow.

That is a different optimization target.

Memory becomes a side effect.

Continuity becomes primary.

